ing the \"tear and stack\" method without the\nneed of any extra tuning of the twist angle and has the advantage that the\nfirst magic angle is always larger than the bilayer case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jan 2019 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2019 21:51:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
